.legwork-survey-container
  header
    h1 Free Dental Implant Assessment
    h3 Take our quick survey to see if dental implants are right for you.
  #form-container
    .row.radio
      h4 1/4
      h2 How many teeth are you missing?
      input(type="radio" name="missingTeeth")
      span A single tooth
      br
      input(type="radio" name="missingTeeth")
      span A few teeth
      br
      input(type="radio" name="missingTeeth")
      span I am without teeth
      br
    .row
      h4 2/4
      h2 Select the options that best describe your biggest concern with your smile.
      .multi-option
        .option
          .checkmark
          p I want to be able to better chew my food
        .option
          .checkmark
          p I want to improve the appearance of my smile
        .option
          .checkmark
          p My dentures don't look and/or don't feel natural
    .row
      h4 3/4
      h2 What, if any, are your biggest concerns with implants?
      .multi-option
        .option
          .checkmark
          p I am concerned whether or not they will last
        .option
          .checkmark
          p I am fearful of the treatment process
        .option
          .checkmark
          p I am not sure I can afford it
        .option
          .checkmark
          p I need more assurance that the dentist is qualified
        .option
          .checkmark
          p I have no real concerns
    .row.submit-info-cta
      h4 5/5
      h2 Provide your name and email to get your results.
      p Your privacy is our utmost concern. Your name and email will not be shared with any third party.
